							<hr />
							<h2 id="purpose">Purpose</h2>
							<p>The purpose of the DARIAH-DE <strong>StyleGuideTemplate</strong> (<strong>SGT</strong> from now on) is to provide a basic template for all web applications that are part of the DARIAH-DE ecosystem.
							</p>
							<div class="alert alert-info">
								<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
								<strong>Tip:</strong> If you are about to start developing a new DARIAH-DE application, by following the SGT the look &amp; feel of your app is going to be consistent with the rest of the applications.
							</div>
							<div class="alert alert-info">
								<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
								<strong>Tip:</strong> If you have already developed a DARIAH-DE application, you may want to adjust its layout so as to match the one described by the SGT.
							</div>
							<h3>Dependencies</h3>
							<p>This template relies on the following external resources:
								<ul>
									<li><a href="http://bootstrapdocs.com/v2.2.2/docs/">Boostrap Framework (v. 2.2)</a></li>
									<li><a href="http://www.jquery.com/">jQuery</a> Library (v. 1.8.2)</li>
									<li><a href="http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/">Font Awesome icons (v. 4.3.0)</a>, e.g. <i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i> <i class="fa fa-globe"></i> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> etc. </li>
									<li><a href="www.famfamfam.com/lab/icons/flags/">FamFamFam flag icons</a>, e.g. <img src="resources/img/famfamfam_flag_icons/png/de.png" alt="German"/> <img src="resources/img/famfamfam_flag_icons/png/gb.png" alt="English"/> <img src="resources/img/famfamfam_flag_icons/png/fr.png" alt="French"/> etc.</li>
								</ul>
							</p>
							<hr />
							<h2 id="howto">How to use this template?</h2>
							<p>Clone the <a href="https://github.com/DARIAH-DE/StyleGuideTemplate">github repository</a> and start adapting the template to your own application (e.g. integration with the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_web_template_engines">template engine</a> of your choice).</p>
							<h3>What to change</h3>
							<p>
								<ul>
									<li>the <strong>tool name</strong></li>
									<li>the <strong>"breadcrumbs"</strong> section</li>
									<li>the list of <strong>supported languages</strong>
										<div class="alert alert-info">
											<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
											<strong>Tip:</strong> To find the language list look for this element in the HTML source code:
											<pre>&lt;ul id="language_selection"&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt;</pre>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li>the <strong>licence</strong> information
									<div class="alert alert-info">
										<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
										<strong>Tip:</strong> Look for this element in the HTML source code:
										<pre>&lt;div id="footer"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
									</div>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</p>
							<h3>What not to change</h3>
							<p><i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i>The DARIAH-DE Global Menu must remain unchanged (i.e. the dropdown menu in the top-left corner which is re-populated from a global JSON definition).</p>
							<hr />
							<h2 id="sgt_content">Content</h2>
							<h3>Templates</h3>
							<p>The <tt>/templates/</tt> directory contains the following template variants:</p>
							<ul>
								<li><tt><a href="notloggedin.html">/templates/notloggedin.html</a></tt>
									: this template assumes that the user <strong>is not</strong> logged in as indicated by the <i class="icon-signin icon-white"></i> icon displayed in the top-right corner</li>
								<li><tt><a href="loggedin.html">/templates/loggedin.html</a></tt>
									: this template assumes that the user <strong>is</strong> logged in as indicated by the <i class="fa-user icon-white"></i> icon displayed in the top-right corner</li>
								<li><tt><a href="withlogo.html">/templates/withlogo.html</a></tt>
									: this is an alternate template that displays the DARIAH-DE logo within the dropdown menu in the top-left corner</li>
							</ul>
							<h3>Resources</h3>
							<p>The <tt>/resources/</tt> directory contains all the files required by the SGT in order to display correctly. </p>
							<p>This directory has the following straight-forward structure:
								<ul>
									<li><tt>/resources/css/</tt></li>
									<li><tt>/resources/fonts/</tt></li>
									<li><tt>/resources/img/</tt></li>
									<li><tt>/resources/js/</tt></li>
								</ul>
							</p>
